# Extra-Files: postinst.sh, debian/control
Postinst: debian/postinst.sh
Prerm: debian/prerm.sh
Depends: php5-cli, curl
Description: Command line TWitter Interface
	twi (aka. TWitter Interface) is single twitter user, multi-unix user, twitter command line client
	meant to be simple to use and send updates quickly. The only additional feature at this time
	is deleting a tweet.
	.
	Twi is written by Jeremy Brand and utilizes Tijs Verkoyen OAuth twitter_oauth class.
	.
	http://www.nirvani.net/software/twi	
